# Lohan Moraes Portfolio

## Stack

- **Runtime / PM**: Bun
- **Framework**: React 19 + Vite+ (`vp` CLI)
- **Routing**: TanStack Router (`src/routes/`)
- **Motion**: Lenis + GSAP ScrollTrigger
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 + Tailwind Variants (`tv`)

## Commands

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Dev server | `bun run dev` |
| Build | `bun run build` |
| Validate | `bun run validate` |

## CI/CD

GitHub Actions (`.github/workflows/deploy.yml`) → GitHub Pages SPA.
